# рҹҡ– Chicago Taxi Trips вҖ” End-to-End Microsoft BI Project

> A complete, production-style Business Intelligence pipeline built from scratch on **100,000+ rows** of real, messy, public data вҖ” covering every layer of the Microsoft BI stack: SQL Server вҶ’ SSIS вҶ’ SSAS вҶ’ SSRS вҶ’ Power BI.

