в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җв”Җ 02_landing_table_ddl.sql             вҶҗ landing.TaxiRaw (raw ingestion shelf)
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җв”Җ 03_usp_CleanTaxi.sql                 вҶҗ Staging cleaning stored procedure
